" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mini-UPS800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mini-UPS800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mini-UPS800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441610" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Volkano-Router-UPS-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Volkano-Router-UPS-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Volkano-Router-UPS-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Volkano-Router-UPS-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441608" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Gizzu-Router-UPS-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Gizzu-Router-UPS-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Gizzu-Router-UPS-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Gizzu-Router-UPS-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441604" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Vizia-UPS800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Vizia-UPS800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Vizia-UPS800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Vizia-UPS800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> With many South Africans still working from home after the Covid-19 lockdowns, a backup system can be critical to power a workstation through load-shedding sessions. On the other hand, load-shedding also makes keeping yourself entertained a struggle. However, several larger UPSes are available in South Africa that can power your TV or computer. It should be noted that battery life will vary based on the voltage demand placed on the UPS. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441618" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Powercom-Raptor-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Powercom-Raptor-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Powercom-Raptor-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Powercom-Raptor-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441624" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Andowl-UPS-80V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Andowl-UPS-80V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Andowl-UPS-80V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Andowl-UPS-80V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441622" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Kstar-UPS-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Kstar-UPS-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.c