South Africans are currently paying R21.63 per litre of unleaded 93. Buyers should also ensure that the generator comes with an automatic voltage regulator if they want to power sensitive electronics with it. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441640" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Omega-generator-1-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Omega-generator-1-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Omega-generator-1-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Omega-generator-1-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441642" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ryobi-950-Gen-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ryobi-950-Gen-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ryobi-950-Gen-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ryobi-950-Gen-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-441638" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ineco-Generator-800V.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="533" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ineco-Generator-800V.jpg 800w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ineco-Generator-800V-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Ineco-Generator-800V-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-44164